description:
Animating very pretty shapes

More lightweight, resulting in great raytracing and CG quality at low stabs and CFGs.

(masterpiece:1.2, best quality:1.1), full body,

Feel free to add more using the Styles feature.

An Extremely Delicate And Beautiful, Best Shadows, Shallow Depth of Field, Brilliant Colorful Paintings, Dramatic Shadow, Dramatic Lighting, sharp focus, (8k), (4k), extremely detailed, intricate, hyper detailed,

Negative prompt

(worst quality:1.4), (low quality:1.4), multiple panels, blurry, bad-hands-5, bad_prompt_version2, multiple panels, blurry, watermark, letterbox, text, ( Poorly Made Bad 3D, Lousy Bad Realistic:1.1 ), From Above, From Below, multiple views:1.4,

- Negative prompt /( From Above, From Below )/ You can leave it out.

Steps : 30 ~ 45 / max 55

CFG : 6~13 / max 22.5
Denoising strength between 0.3 ~ 0.5
i'm love 0.4 and 0.5
Clip skip : 2



Purple Eyes -Settings

Detection Detailer - bbox\mmdet_anime-face_yolov3.pth

CFG 8~15
I'm CFG 15 love

3

Good luck with your images! :D

We'll be back with more great models!

Have a great day.

modelVersions.description:
This model is a merge model that is lighter and made with more data than the previously deployed first generation model.

It has a better animation style than the first generation model.

This model comes from an unpublished merge model and a merge of other models.
